5 Section 2.
6
7 (a) Eight hundred thousand dollars ($800,000.00) is
8 appropriated from the general fund to the legislative
9 service office to fund the model recalibration study in
10 accordance with section 1 of this act. Funds appropriated
11 under this section shall be expended in accordance with a
12 contractual agreement entered into between the management
13 council and professional consultants to the legislature for
14 recalibration of the education resource block grant model.
15 This appropriation shall be for the period beginning with
16 the effective date of this act and ending June 30, 2026.
17 This appropriation shall not be transferred or expended for
18 any other purpose and any unexpended, unobligated funds
19 remaining from this appropriation shall revert as provided
20 by law on June 30, 2026.
21
22 (b) One hundred twenty thousand dollars ($120,000.00)
23 is appropriated from the general fund to the legislative
